    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled distinction. This vehicle has been maintained to the most exacting standards, retaining its original showroom luster and mechanical precision. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a legacy of meticulous care. We invite the discerning buyer to experience a motorcar that transcends the typical pre-owned market, offering a level of refinement and reliability that is truly exceptional. This is an investment-grade vehicle prepared for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
