    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is an superlative example of the naturally aspirated 3.8L DFI flat-six era, paired with a sought-after 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is absolute, featuring PASM active damping and a limited-slip differential for optimized lateral grip and turn-in precision. Every component, from the multi-piston monobloc calipers to the pristine undercarriage, reflects a rigorous maintenance schedule and climate-controlled storage. With no bore scoring, a flawless Rev Range report, and original paint depth throughout, this is a concours-ready specimen for the serious collector.",
